{"title":"Vueд№Ӣkeep-aliveдҪҝз”ЁжҢҮеҚ—","date":"2020-01-16T08:11:00.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"Jan 16, 2020","L":"01/16/2020","MM-DD":"01-16"},"author":"Yx1aoq1","link":"2020/01/16/Vueд№Ӣkeep-alive","tags":["Vue"],"categories":["Vueзӣёе…і"],"updated":"2020-05-31T15:11:17.417Z","content":"<h2 id=\"йңҖжұӮ\">йңҖжұӮ<a title=\"#йңҖжұӮ\" href=\"#йңҖжұӮ\"></a></h2>\n<p>еңЁеҒҡдёҡеҠЎзҡ„ж—¶еҖҷз»Ҹеёёдјҡзў°еҲ°иҝҷж ·зҡ„дә’еҠЁйңҖжұӮпјҡ</p>\n<ul>\n<li>з”ЁжҲ·еүҚиҝӣж—¶пјҢжҖ»жҳҜиҝӣе…ҘдёҖдёӘж–°зҡ„йЎөйқўпјҲдёҚдҪҝз”Ёзј“еӯҳпјү</li>\n<li>з”ЁжҲ·еҗҺйҖҖж—¶пјҢйңҖиҰҒдҝқз•ҷд№ӢеүҚзҡ„ж“ҚдҪңпјҲдҪҝз”Ёзј“еӯҳпјү</li>\n</ul>\n<p>еңЁ<code>vue-router</code>дёӯпјҢеҲҮжҚўи·Ҝз”ұж—¶е№¶дёҚдјҡдҝқеӯҳз»„д»¶зҡ„зҠ¶жҖҒпјҢиҖҢжҳҜдјҡйҮҚж–°еҲӣе»әж–°з»„д»¶пјҢиө°дёҖйҒҚе®Ңж•ҙзҡ„з”ҹе‘Ҫе‘ЁжңҹпјҢжҲ‘д»¬иҰҒе®һзҺ°дёҠйқўзҡ„йңҖжұӮпјҢе°ұйңҖиҰҒдҪҝз”Ё<code>keep-alive</code>з»„д»¶жқҘи§ЈеҶігҖӮ</p>\n<h2 id=\"keep-alive\"><a href=\"https://cn.vuejs.org/v2/api/#keep-alive\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">keep-alive</a><a title=\"#keep-alive\" href=\"#keep-alive\"></a></h2>\n<p>йҖҡиҝҮз»“еҗҲ<code>router-view</code>жҲ‘д»¬е°ұеҸҜд»Ҙе®һзҺ°зј“еӯҳйЎөйқўзҡ„й—®йўҳпјҡ</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight html\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">keep-alive</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">router-view</span> <span class=\"attr\">v-if</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"isKeepAlive\"</span> <span class=\"attr\">:key</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"keepAliveKey\"</span> <span class=\"attr\">transition</span> <span class=\"attr\">transition-mode</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"out-in\"</span>&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">router-view</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">keep-alive</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">router-view</span> <span class=\"attr\">v-if</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"!isKeepAlive\"</span> <span class=\"attr\">transition</span> <span class=\"attr\">transition-mode</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"out-in\"</span>&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">router-view</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p><code>isKeepAlive</code>зҡ„еҲӨж–ӯеҸҜд»ҘйҖҡиҝҮ<code>$route.meta</code>жқҘй…ҚзҪ®е“Әдәӣи·Ҝз”ұйңҖиҰҒзј“еӯҳпјҢиҖҢ<code>keepAliveKey</code>еҸҜд»Ҙз®ҖеҚ•зҡ„дҪҝз”Ё<code>$route.fullPath</code>пјҢж №жҚ®дҪҝз”ЁеңәжҷҜиҖҢе®ҡгҖӮ</p>\n<p>еӣ дёәдҪҝз”ЁдәҶ<code>keep-alive</code>пјҢдёҚи®әжҳҜеүҚиҝӣиҝҳжҳҜеҗҺйҖҖпјҢжҲ‘д»¬жҖ»дјҡиҝӣе…ҘеҲ°зј“еӯҳзҡ„з»„д»¶пјҢйӮЈд№ҲжҖҺд№ҲжүҚиғҪиҝӣе…Ҙж–°йЎөйқўе‘ўпјҹйҰ–е…ҲеҸҜд»ҘжғіеҲ°зҡ„жҳҜдҪҝз”Ё<code>$destroy</code>еҲ йҷӨз»„д»¶пјҢдҪҶжҳҜе®һйҷ…ж“ҚдҪңзҡ„ж—¶еҖҷеҸ‘зҺ°зј“еӯҳдҫқз„¶еӯҳеңЁгҖӮдәҺжҳҜйҖҡиҝҮдёҮиғҪзҡ„жҗңзҙўжүҫеҲ°дәҶдёҖдёӘи§ЈеҶіж–№жЎҲпјҡ<a href=\"https://juejin.im/post/5b610da4e51d45195c07720d#heading-1\" target=\"_blank\">Vue е…Ёз«ҷзј“еӯҳд№Ӣ keep-alive пјҡ еҠЁжҖҒз§»йҷӨзј“еӯҳ</a></p>\n<p>з®ҖиҖҢиЁҖд№Ӣе°ұжҳҜйңҖиҰҒиҮӘе·ұжүҫеҲ°<code>keep-alive</code>зҡ„е®һдҫӢжүӢеҠЁеҲ йҷӨпјҢе№¶й”ҖжҜҒз»„д»¶гҖӮ</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight js\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">const</span> destroy = <span class=\"function\">(<span class=\"params\">key</span>) =&gt;</span> &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"comment\">// жүҫеҲ°keepAliveз»„д»¶</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"keyword\">const</span> keepAliveVm = global.keepAliveVm <span class=\"comment\">// е…·дҪ“жҖҺд№ҲжүҫеҲ°keeyAliveз»„д»¶иҮӘе·ұзңӢжғ…еҶө</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"keyword\">const</span> cache = keepAliveVm.cache</span><br><span class=\"line\">  cosnt keys = keepAliveVm.keys</span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"comment\">// еҲ йҷӨkeys</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> (keys.indexOf(key) &gt; <span class=\"number\">-1</span>) keys.splice(keys.indexOf(key), <span class=\"number\">1</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"comment\">// еҲ йҷӨcache</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"keyword\">delete</span> cache[key]</span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"comment\">// $destroyз»„д»¶</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  vnodes[key].$destroy()</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>в–ј <strong>жіЁж„ҸзӮ№пјҡ</strong> еңЁдҪҝз”Ё<code>max</code>ж—¶еҗҢж ·дјҡеӯҳеңЁзј“еӯҳдёҚеҲ йҷӨзҡ„жғ…еҶөпјҢйңҖиҰҒиҮӘе·ұжүӢеҠЁеҲ йҷӨгҖӮ</p>\n<h2 id=\"йңҖжұӮе®һзҺ°\">йңҖжұӮе®һзҺ°<a title=\"#йңҖжұӮе®һзҺ°\" href=\"#йңҖжұӮе®һзҺ°\"></a></h2>\n<h3 id=\"еҰӮдҪ•еҲӨж–ӯйЎөйқўзҡ„еүҚиҝӣеҗҺйҖҖ\">еҰӮдҪ•еҲӨж–ӯйЎөйқўзҡ„еүҚиҝӣеҗҺйҖҖ<a title=\"#еҰӮдҪ•еҲӨж–ӯйЎөйқўзҡ„еүҚиҝӣеҗҺйҖҖ\" href=\"#еҰӮдҪ•еҲӨж–ӯйЎөйқўзҡ„еүҚиҝӣеҗҺйҖҖ\"></a></h3>\n<p>жҲ‘д»¬еҸҜд»ҘеңЁй…ҚзҪ®и·Ҝз”ұж—¶пјҢз»ҷжҜҸдёӘйЎөйқўи®ҫзҪ®еұӮзә§е…ізі»пјҡ</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight js\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">routes: [</span><br><span class=\"line\">  &#123; <span class=\"attr\">path</span>: <span class=\"string\">'/list'</span>, <span class=\"attr\">component</span>: List, <span class=\"attr\">meta</span>: &#123; <span class=\"attr\">level</span>: <span class=\"number\">1</span> &#125; &#125;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">  &#123; <span class=\"attr\">path</span>: <span class=\"string\">'/edit'</span>, <span class=\"attr\">component</span>: Edit, <span class=\"attr\">meta</span>: &#123; <span class=\"attr\">level</span>: <span class=\"number\">2</span> &#125; &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>з„¶еҗҺеңЁVueе…ЁеұҖжіЁеҶҢдёҖдёӘж··е…Ҙж–№жі•пјҢеңЁжҜҸж¬Ўи·Ҝз”ұеҲҮжҚўзҡ„ж—¶еҖҷеҲӨж–ӯеұӮзә§еҸҳеҢ–пјҢжҺ§еҲ¶жҳҜеҗҰиҰҒеҲ йҷӨзј“еӯҳпјҡ</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight js\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">Vue.mixin(&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  befroeRouteLeave (to, <span class=\"keyword\">from</span>, next) &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> (<span class=\"keyword\">from</span> &amp;&amp; <span class=\"keyword\">from</span>.meta.level &amp;&amp; to.meta.level &amp;&amp; <span class=\"keyword\">from</span>.meta.level &gt; to.meta.level) &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">      <span class=\"comment\">// еҰӮжһңжҳҜеҗҺйҖҖпјҢеҲҷеҲ йҷӨз»„д»¶зј“еӯҳ</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">      <span class=\"keyword\">const</span> keepAliveVm = <span class=\"keyword\">this</span>.$vnode.parent.componentInstance</span><br><span class=\"line\">      <span class=\"keyword\">const</span> &#123; keys, cache &#125; = keepAliveVm</span><br><span class=\"line\">      <span class=\"keyword\">const</span> key = <span class=\"keyword\">this</span>.$route.fullPath</span><br><span class=\"line\">      <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> (keys.indexOf(key) &gt; <span class=\"number\">-1</span>) keys.splice(keys.indexOf(key), <span class=\"number\">1</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\">      <span class=\"keyword\">delete</span> cache[key]</span><br><span class=\"line\">      <span class=\"keyword\">this</span>.$destroy()</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h3 id=\"еҰӮдҪ•и§ҰеҸ‘зј“еӯҳйЎөйқўж•°жҚ®зҡ„жӣҙж–°\">еҰӮдҪ•и§ҰеҸ‘зј“еӯҳйЎөйқўж•°жҚ®зҡ„жӣҙж–°<a title=\"#еҰӮдҪ•и§ҰеҸ‘зј“еӯҳйЎөйқўж•°жҚ®зҡ„жӣҙж–°\" href=\"#еҰӮдҪ•и§ҰеҸ‘зј“еӯҳйЎөйқўж•°жҚ®зҡ„жӣҙж–°\"></a></h3>\n<p>еҰӮжһңдҪҝз”ЁдәҶ<code>keep-alive</code>пјҢеҶҚйҮҚж–°жёІжҹ“иҝҷдёӘз»„д»¶зҡ„ж—¶еҖҷдёҚдјҡеҶҚи§ҰеҸ‘з”ҹе‘Ҫе‘Ёжңҹзҡ„<code>created</code>е’Ң<code>mounted</code>пјҢиҖҢжҳҜи§ҰеҸ‘<code>activated</code>гҖӮжүҖд»ҘжҲ‘д»¬еҸҜд»ҘеңЁ<code>activated</code>дёӯеҺ»жү§иЎҢжҲ‘д»¬жғіиҰҒзҡ„ж•°жҚ®жӣҙж–°пјҡ</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight js\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">Vue.mixin(&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  created () &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">this</span>.pageEnter &amp;&amp; <span class=\"keyword\">this</span>.pageEnter()</span><br><span class=\"line\">  &#125;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">  activated () &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">this</span>.pageEnter &amp;&amp; <span class=\"keyword\">this</span>.pageEnter()</span><br><span class=\"line\">  &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>","prev":{"title":"гҖҗз®—жі•гҖ‘жҺ’еәҸз®—жі•жҖ»з»“","link":"2020/05/28/гҖҗз®—жі•гҖ‘жҺ’еәҸз®—жі•жҖ»з»“"},"next":{"title":"Hexoд№ӢеҰӮдҪ•еңЁзәҝзј–иҫ‘еҚҡе®ў","link":"2020/01/09/Hexoд№ӢеҰӮдҪ•еңЁзәҝзј–иҫ‘еҚҡе®ў"},"plink":"http://yoursite.com/2020/01/16/Vueд№Ӣkeep-alive/","toc":[{"id":"йңҖжұӮ","title":"йңҖжұӮ","index":"1"},{"id":"keep-alive","title":"keep-alive","index":"2"},{"id":"йңҖжұӮе®һзҺ°","title":"йңҖжұӮе®һзҺ°","index":"3","children":[{"id":"еҰӮдҪ•еҲӨж–ӯйЎөйқўзҡ„еүҚиҝӣеҗҺйҖҖ","title":"еҰӮдҪ•еҲӨж–ӯйЎөйқўзҡ„еүҚиҝӣеҗҺйҖҖ","index":"3.1"},{"id":"еҰӮдҪ•и§ҰеҸ‘зј“еӯҳйЎөйқўж•°жҚ®зҡ„жӣҙж–°","title":"еҰӮдҪ•и§ҰеҸ‘зј“еӯҳйЎөйқўж•°жҚ®зҡ„жӣҙж–°","index":"3.2"}]}],"copyright":{"author":"Yx1aoq1","link":"<a href=\"http://yoursite.com/2020/01/16/Vueд№Ӣkeep-alive/\" title=\"Vueд№Ӣkeep-aliveдҪҝз”ЁжҢҮеҚ—\">http://yoursite.com/2020/01/16/Vueд№Ӣkeep-alive/</a>","license":"Attribution-NonCommercial-NoDerivatives 4.0 International (<a href=\"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/4.0/\" rel=\"external nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">CC BY-NC-ND 4.0</a>)"}}